acts of helping little girls you know i mean she's got the burning rain she's lost in the sahara desert and once she finds a little girl who's even more burned than she is you know has to scoop her up and and and you know that their their clothes get torn on a cactus you know but the the little girl this is what's interesting this actually the burning rain is a very

