And so I just pulled out my computer, and I think my son was asleep in the back, and we were just doing errands.

54:01.379 --> 54:04.424
And so I just typed it out as she dictated the story.

54:04.624 --> 54:05.565
So you stopped the card?

54:05.585 --> 54:12.315
Stopped the card, typed it out, and I think she felt very relieved, you know, that I had... That you'd recorded it?

54:12.435 --> 54:15.660
Recorded it.

