And I know she's pleased.

54:18.054 --> 54:19.836
That's one of the things she's read in the book.

54:19.856 --> 54:29.007
She hasn't read the book from cover to cover, but she's very pleased that some of her stories are in there, more or less, that she told them.

54:29.027 --> 54:32.651
Did you discuss with her while this was in process that you're using her?

54:32.871 --> 54:36.876
Yeah, because I wouldn't have used... That's an important question.

54:36.896 --> 54:39.259
Yeah, I asked her... You need her permission, I think.

